\id 3JN ‑ Ikizu 3 John
\h 3 Yoohana
\toc3 3 Yoohana
\toc2 3 Yoohana
\toc1 Ɨnyarʉbha ya katatʉ ya Yoohana
\mt2 Ɨnyarʉbha ya katatʉ ya
\mt1 Yoohana
\imt1 Ʉbhʉkangati
\ip Mʉnyarʉbha ya katatʉ, Yoohana araandɨkɨra ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ aarɨ arabhirikirwa Gaayo. Gaayo aarɨ bhwɨma bhʉkʉngʼu ku kwisirirya Kiriisitʉ. Aarɨ arabhasakirya abhiija abhandɨ bhanʉ bhaarɨ bhariiruguura ahagero hayo, igʉrʉ wʉ ʉkʉnyaraganʼya Amaandɨkʉ Amazʉmu. Yoohana aramwandɨkɨra komoha umwʉyʉ angʼehe kʉbhasakirya abhiija bhayo.
\ip Kʉnyarʉbha yɨnʉ, Yoohana aragamba ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ aarɨ arabhirikirwa Diyʉtirefe. Ʉmʉʉtʉ wʉnʉ, aarɨ aragema korecha abhaatʉ bha risengerero, bhataginihya abhiija bhanʉ bhaarɨ bhariija Amaandɨkʉ Amazʉmu. Mbarɨka neewe, Yoohana aratora ʉmʉʉtʉ ʉmʉzʉmu wʉnʉ akwikara kwa amaheene, iriina ryazɨ Dɨmɨtiriyʉ.
\c 1
\s1 Amakeerenʼya
\p 
\v 1 Niinyɨ umwimiiririri wa risengerero, nɨrakwandɨkɨra awɨ Gaayo mʉsaani waanɨ. Nɨkʉsɨɨgirɨ kwa amaheene.
\p 
\v 2 Nangʉ, ʉmʉsɨɨgwa waanɨ, nɨrakʉsabhɨra kwa Mungu ʉbhɨ mʉhʉru, na amangʼana gaazʉ gʉʉsi gajɨ bhwaheene, chɨmbu okongʼeha mʉmangʼana ga mokoro.
\v 3 Nɨkazomerwa bhʉkʉngʼu, hanʉ abhahiiri bhiizirɨ ɨnʉ na kʉmbʉʉrɨra awɨ ʉrakaja kugwata amaheene, na kwikara kʉmaheene.
\v 4 Kɨtareeho ekegero kɨnʉ kekongʼa obhozomerwa bhʉkʉngʼu kʉkɨra kwigwa, abhaana bhaanɨ bharakaja kwikara kʉmaheene.
\s1 Obhoronge bhwa Gaayo
\p 
\v 5 Mʉsaani waanɨ, awɨ ne‑moheene kʉganʉ ʉkʉbhakorera abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ mubhwisirirya, nangabha nɨ‑bhagini kwa naawɨ.
\v 6 Abhahiiri bhayo bhamɨnyɨɨkɨrɨɨryɨ abhaatʉ bha mwisengerero hanʉ, igʉrʉ wʉ ʉbhʉsɨɨgi bhwazʉ. Nɨrakwisasaama, ʉkajɨ kʉbhasakirya koteemwa yɨnʉ ekozomera Mungu, korereke bhangʼehe no orogendo rwabhʉ.
\v 7 Bhakatanga orogendo rwabhʉ kohokerya Yɨɨsu Kiriisitʉ bhatiisiriiryɨ ʉbhʉsakirya bhwʉbhwʉsi bhwa abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhatɨɨzɨ Mungu.
\v 8 Mmbe itwɨ toreenderwa kʉbhasakirya abhaatʉ ncha bhayo. Ko kokora gayo, tʉrakora hamwɨmwɨ neebho emeremo jʉ ʉkʉraganʼya amaheene.
\s1 Diyʉtirefe na Dɨmɨtiriyʉ
\p 
\v 9 Nɨkaandɨkɨra risengerero ɨnyarʉbha nguhɨ, nawe Diyʉtirefe asɨɨgirɨ kwitʉʉra mʉbhʉtangɨ kina newe ʉmʉkangati wa bhʉʉsi, atakwisirirya ʉbhʉnaja bhwɨtʉ.
\v 10 Mmbe, hanʉ nikuuza iyo, nɨrahumbura amangʼana gʉʉsi ganʉ akokora na chɨmbu akuhurucha ekerege igʉrʉ wɨɨtʉ kʉmangʼana amabhɨ. Gatarɨ gayo ageene, na araanga kuginihya abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ mubhwisirirya. Na abhaatʉ bhanʉ bhakwenda kuginihya abhahiiri bhɨɨtʉ, ewe arabharecha na kʉbhaheebha bharwɨ mwisengerero.
\p 
\v 11 Nangʉ Gaayo, ʉmʉsɨɨgwa waanɨ, ʉtɨɨga amangʼana amabhɨ, nawe wɨɨgɨ amangʼana amazʉmu. Wʉwʉʉsi wʉnʉ akokora amazʉmu, wuyo ni‑mwana wa Mungu. Nawe wʉnʉ akokora amabhɨ, wuyo atɨɨzɨ Mungu.
\p 
\v 12 Abhaatʉ bhʉʉsi bhamɨnyɨɨkɨrɨɨryɨ kʉbha Dɨmɨtiriyʉ nɨ‑mʉʉtʉ mʉzʉmu, nu ubhwikari bhwazɨ bhʉrɨngʼɨɨnɨ na amaheene. Nʉʉrʉ na niitwɨ, tʉramenyeekereryabhu, na ʉmɨnyirɨ kʉbha ʉbhʉmɨnyɨɨkɨrɨri bhwɨtʉ bhwa amaheene.
\s1 Amakeerenʼya gʉ ʉkʉraga
\p 
\v 13 Nɨna amangʼana maaru gʉ ʉkʉgamba, nawe nɨtakwenda kwandɨka kʉnzɨra yɨ ɨnyarʉbha.
\v 14 Kutiga gayo niriisega kʉkʉtaarɨra haguhɨbhu na kwibhisirya hamwɨmwɨ.
\p 
\v 15 Omorembe gʉbhɨ hamwɨmwɨ na naawɨ. Abhasaani bhaazʉ bharakokeerya. Na naawɨ, ʉbhakeerye abhasaani bhɨɨtʉ bhʉʉsibhu kʉmariina gaabhʉ.
